narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: small assignments, peer conversations, and office hours were helpful. guest scholars, analyzing essays, and meeting weekly were not. this class should meet less often, because work time is more helpful than trying to fill time.
class required for ERM seniors to help you finish your senior project
If you are an ER&M major trying to produce a project that you can be proud of at the end of your four years, ER&M 491 is the perfect guide to achieve your goal.
I would definitely recommend this course. The work is manageable, practical, and useful. The discussions are great and the professors were very helpful.
